$1 : 5000$ means 1 cm represents 5000 cm
$\therefore$ 1 cm represents $(5000 \div 100)$ m {100 cm $= 1$ m}
$\therefore$ 1 cm represents 50 m

actual length $= \text{drawn length} \times 500000$ {scale factor 500000}
$\therefore$ actual length $= 15$ cm $\times 500000$
$= 7500000$ cm
$= (7500000 \div 100)$ m {1 m $= 100$ cm}
$= 75000$ m
$= (75000 \div 1000)$ km {1 km $= 1000$ m}
$\therefore$ actual length $= 75$ km
